# Question Template: During {EVENT_WINDOW}, which {IMAGE_TYPE} scenes line up with outage snapshots for {PLACE_DESCRIPTOR}?
# Label: Spatiotemporal interpretation: landfall-centered two-day snapshot window
# Ambiguity Dimensions: spatiotemporal, temporal
# Rationale: Allows the landfall-date wording to include immediate post-landfall snapshots while preserving the same Lee County scope.
PREFIX goo:    <https://ucf-henat.github.io/GeoOutageOnto/#>
