# Label: Primary interpretation: Lee County severity maps in an Ian-centered impact window
# Ambiguity Dimensions: spatiotemporal, temporal, semantic
# Rationale: Matches the edited question by returning outage-severity maps for the Fort Myers-area county during an Ian-centered window, without requiring an outage-record join.
