# Question: Which remote sensing machine and instrument captured any random nighttime-light image in the GeoOutage dataset?
# Question Template: Which {PLATFORM_TYPE} and {SENSOR_TYPE} captured any {IMAGE_TYPE} image in {DATASET}?
# Label: Primary interpretation: platform and sensor for one arbitrary NTL image
