# Query 29
# QID: 1000021
# Interpretation ID: Q1000021_I0
# Interpretation Type: original source query
# Template ID: T004
# Template Family: multimodal_correspondence
# Question: Which U.S. county is depicted in the power outage severity map corresponding to a specific customer outage record?
# Question Template: Which {JURISDICTION_TYPE} is depicted in the {MAP_TYPE} corresponding to {OUTAGE_RECORD}?
# Label: Original exact KG interpretation from source JSON
# Ambiguity Dimensions: spatiotemporal
# Rationale: Preserves the original SPARQL query exactly as supplied in the source GeoOutageBench JSON.
PREFIX goo:    <https://ucf-henat.github.io/GeoOutageOnto/#>
