# Query 31
# QID: 1000023
# Interpretation ID: Q1000023_I0
# Interpretation Type: original source query
# Template ID: T004
# Template Family: multimodal_correspondence
# Question: Is there an EAGLE-I snapshot for the Tampa, Florida county that also has a matching NTL scene?
# Question Template: Is there an {OUTAGE_RECORD_SOURCE} snapshot for {JURISDICTION_INSTANCE} that also has a matching {IMAGE_TYPE} scene?
# Label: Primary interpretation: same-day EAGLE-I outage snapshot and NTL scene for Hillsborough County
# Ambiguity Dimensions: spatiotemporal, semantic
# Rationale: Aligns the interpretation text with the edited Tampa/Hillsborough County yes-no matching question; the ASK pattern already encodes that match.
